Holly Willoughby looked sensational as she celebrated her 42nd birthday in style. The This Morning presenter took to Instagram to share a glowing snap of herself surrounded by birthday balloons and holding a pink bouquet. She penned in the caption: "It’s my BIRTHDAY!!! Thank you for all your kind wishes… what a beautiful day … the best birthday gift of glorious blue skies and sunshine… with a healthy side/slab of cake." (sic) Holly also shared a selection of the birthday messages she had received from her famous pals. Phillip Schofield shared a sunny photo of the pair to mark his "gorgeous" friend's birthday. Spice Girl Emma Bunton, Kate Thornton, and Josie Gibson also took to social media to mark Holly's special day.